Interface ActionSourceAttachedObjectTarget

All Superinterfaces:

public interface ActionSourceAttachedObjectTarget extends AttachedObjectTarget

A marker interface for VDL tags that represent <composite:actionSource/> for use by the composite component page author.

Historical note: this class was previously named ActionSource2AttachedObjectTarget but since deprecation of ActionSource2 this class has been renamed to drop the 2.

Since:
4.1
